[[Category: Cities]]

{{DISPLAYTITLE:Eastwalk Duchy}}

The south-eastern duchy of the [[Duarchy of Kotimaa]]. Almost entirely rural and feeling the effects of the [[Winter War]] and the withdrawal of the [[Holy Kaelthian Republic]], with which it had had significant cultural ties. Human-dominated in the northern area with extensive halfling populations near the former border. Culturally by far the most traditionalist and religious (almost to the point of zealotry) of the duchies.

